entry.tp - Touch Portal Plugin Entry Point

This is the entry point for the ESP8266 Light Controller Touch Portal Plugin.

The actual plugin execution is handled by plugin.py as specified in manifest.json.

Plugin Information:
- Name: ESP8266 Light Controller
- Version: 1.0.0
- Category: ESP Camera Light
- Description: Control WS2812B addressable LED strip on ESP8266 via HTTP API
- Author: foloryx

Supported Actions:
1. Light ON - Turn on the light
2. Light OFF - Turn off the light
3. Set Brightness - Set brightness level (0-100%)

Connectors:
- Brightness Slider (0-100) - Real-time brightness adjustment

States:
- Light State - Current state of the light (On/Off)
- Brightness - Current brightness level (0-100)

Configuration Requirements:
- ESP8266 IP Address
- Port (default: 80)
- Connection Timeout (default: 5 seconds)

API Endpoints Used:
- GET /api/on - Turn light on
- GET /api/off - Turn light off
- GET /api/brightness?value=0-255 - Set brightness

For installation and setup instructions, see README.md
